wikibase-listdatatypes-globe-coordinate-:
kahicelaan kakitizaan a sulit kalunasulitan nay wyitu - cintu napalekal, pisaungay gms saca bataan-cumut-enengan tikenih nay pakatineng kakitizaan nu ipabaw nu bunac-kitakit. hina tuzu’ " puenengan kanatal " zumasatu pisaungay "WGS84" taenengan sisetyimo. kya taenengan sisetyimo macunutu ku katingalaw atu subal.
*  wyitu – taenengan ilabu’ nu sulisulitan sakacacay a liyad (float, dms, dm, dd)，pasayzaan i saayaway sulit saca sazikuzay a sulit pisaungay N saca S pakatineng
*  cintu – taenengan ilabu’ nu sasulitan sakatusa a liyad (float, dms, dm, dd)，pasayzaan i saayaway sulit saca sazikuzay a sulit pisaungay E saca W pakatineng
*  uzip nu bunac – sawantan (?) a sulyang, pataayaw tu kawaw matuzu’ay a bunac-kitakit ku " puenengan kitakit " "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q2" 
*  sanat-masitudung-ditek –  taenengan a asip-bacu sanat-masitudung-ditek
wikibase-listdatatypes-quantity-body:
atu hatizaay mapulita satetek a tatebanan nu nisulitan mahizaay a nikayadah sulit kalunasulitan pisinga’an. tatena’ay tatebanan nu nisulitan yamalyilu i nasulitan a kalunasulitan sulyang.

* nikayadah – layad nu sulisulitan (patatapalenay tatebanan nu nisulitan saayaway suli caay kapulita ) 
* tatebanan nu nisulitan – layad nu sulisulitan, pataayaw tu kawaw ku "1" (patatapalenay tatungusay a kuwanay caay kapulita ) 
* pabaw-sahezek sulyang - nikayadah a pabaw-sahezek
* sainayi'ay a sulyang - nikayadah a saingay’ay
wikibase-listdatatypes-monolingualtext-b:
cacay kanca mibelih tu zumaay kamu a sulisulitan a saayaway kalunasulitan sulit-ngatu. u tilid ku sikawaw i caay kalecaday a sulit-kakuniza i niyazu’, uyzasa singangan i kitakit mahmin masaheciay kalungangan. hakay ku heni i kamu atu sulit sisetyimo caay kalecad. 
* kamu–mibacu liyad nu cudad kamu nu siwantan a sulyang 
* sulyang–uzumaay kamu masazumaay sulit-bacu-sulsul siwantan a sulyang
wikibase-listdatatypes-string-body:
tatebanan nu nisulitan a saayaway kalunasulitan sulit-ngatu. tiliday a sadama tu kawaw sa atu miasipay a kamu inayi’ mahizaay a sulit sasakawawen a sacuzu’-bacu.
* cudad – uzumaay a kamu masazumaay sulisulitan sawantanay a sulyang
wikibase-listdatatypes-url-body: cacay URL a sulit tatebanan nu nisulitan. URL mapakelec ihekal masasiketay sasakawawen masulit ilabu’ nu Wiki a sulit.
wikibase-concept-uri-tooltip: URI amitaazih tina kasacacay masapuelac a nizatengan

right-property-term: misumad susin a kamu (aazihen-paya, sapuelac atu pacimilay ngangan)
